        <r:Description>
            <r:Content>Required: Mandatory if 'keyword' element is present</r:Content>
            <r:Content>ElementType: Attribute</r:Content>
            <r:Content>Usage: Language of the keyword. ISO 639-1 codes are strongly encouraged to be
